<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using a non XHTML doctype such as HTML4_STRICT, the doctype header generated by the view helper adds invalid attributes to the  tag.</p>

<p>Using &lt;?php echo $this-&gt;doctype() ?&gt; will generate the following invalid markup</p>

<p>www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en"&gt;</p>

<p>Both xmlns and xml:lang are not valid attributes for HTML4 Strict.</p>

<p>Run pages through w3c validator as a confirmation when using HTML4_STRICT</p>

