        <div class="body">
            <p>You have misconstrued the usage of the doctype() helper. The helper serves two purposes, and two purposes only:
* Echo out the selected doctype string (and allow selection of said string using mnemonics)
* Hint to various doctype-aware helpers the general doctype -- primarily to determine what style closing tag to generate.
It is <em>not</em> intended as a filter to ensure the final document validates against the W3C specifications.</p>

